Package org.opennars.entity

Class Item<K>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opennars.entity.Item<K>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Concept, Item.StringKeyItem, Task, TaskLink, TermLink
    public abstract class Item<K>
extends Object
implements Serializable
    An item is an object that can be put into a Bag, to participate in the resource competition of the system.

    It has a key and a budget. Cannot be cloned

    Author:
    Pei Wang, Patrick Hammer
    See Also:
